long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing the Ultimate Coordinate Converter for Google Maps

Are you tired of manually converting geographic coordinates into Degrees, Minutes, and Seconds (DMS) format to use them effectively on Google Maps? Look no further! Our cutting-edge browser extension is here to simplify the process for you.

Key Features:
- Effortless Conversion: One-click conversion of coordinates to DMS format.
- Search and Convert: Input specific latitude and longitude for quick conversions.
- Time-Saving: Save time and eliminate manual conversions.
- Precision: Ensure accuracy in your location data on Google Maps.

Simplicity and efficiency for DMS conversions on Google Maps. Try it now!
